                  <provenance>Owners Walda Mikāʾel, Walatta Śǝllāse, Za-Walda
                     Māryām, Walatta Wāhǝd, Walda ʾIyasus, Walatta Nǝgǝśt are mentioned in the
                     supplication formulas and in the subscription on <locus target="#128v">128vb-vc</locus>. According to the subscription, Walatta Nǝgǝśt is the
                     owner of the book, her father is Walda Mikāʾel, her mother is Walatta Śǝllāse,
                     her daughter is Walatta Wahǝd and Za-Walda Māryām is the one who intermediated
                     for the acquisition of the book.</provenance>
